description:
The owner of this award has proven to be a huge collector. He was among the first 10 collectors to collect a full *Regular Deck (cards 1-100 including card 42) and a full IOTA Community Hero Deck (Community Hero Card 1-10). This distinguishes him and entitles him to own one of the "Trading Collectors Cards" limited to 10 pieces.

*The ownership of a Regular Collectors Card is represented the ownership of 100 Cards of the Regular Deck. If you have the Regular Collectors Card, I will not further check if the Regular Deck is (still) complete! ;)
name: Trading Collector
